==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: free-thinking
<hw>free-thinking</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>inclined to forms one's own
opinions rather than depend upon authority, especially about social and
religious issues; exhibiting boldness of speculation; skeptical of
authority.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> latitudinarian, undogmatic, undogmatical.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> + <source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Free-tongued</ent>⟦br⟧
